reviews.review_text: Grateful Matthew Vernon you are a hero for putting all these jams up. I can't believe I'm the only one with the kudos. I was at all the alpine shows all the years the were allowed to play there. What a great trip down memory lane. I knew Brent personally and all the times I here his keys it gives me great feelings of friendship and admiration and the thought I was lucky to have known him for as long as I did. Besides listening to the great music.thank you Matt very on you are a hero.
